snippet.title: Eden Survivors — Gameplay Teaser | Survivors-like
snippet.description:
Welcome, hackers, you're being transferred to Eden City to defend its citizens against the alien threat! Eden Survivors is a single-player survivor-like auto-shooter where players must defeat hordes of alien invaders until the extraction time.

Coming soon in Early Access. Wishlist now!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3073350/Eden_Survivors/
